data.description: Move in ready! Come and take a look at this beautiful home in the Pheasant Chase subdivision! This home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and an unfinished basement that is waiting for your personal touch! Open kitchen concept with stainless steel appliances! The home has plenty of space and lots of natural light! Great size backyard with plenty of room for the kids and pets and there is deck that is perfect for family BBQ's and get togethers. There is also a shed in the back yard for extra storage space so you can take full advantage of the space in your 2 car garage!
